nodes.text: Fend'Allomin was a Twi'lek female who lived during the time of the Clone Wars. Much of Fend'Allomin's origins were unknown, except for the fact that she had been a slave for the vast majority of her life. At some point during the early years of her adult life, Fend'Allomin was rescued from slavery by Jedi Master Vhiin Thorla and taken to the hidden settlement known as The Enclave, with several others of her kind.
